<view class="pd-top-20 pd-bottom-20 align-center display-col">
  <text class="fs-warning">距结束仅剩</text>
  <text class="fs-content">{{order.leftTime_d}} 天 {{wxTimer}}</text>
</view>
<view class="wrapper">
  <view class="panel detail">
    <image src="{{order.imageSingle}}"/>
    <view class="content">
      <text class="title">{{order.prdName}}</text>
      <text class="desc">有效期自购买起 {{order.validDays}} 天内有效</text>
      <view class="buying-info">
        <view class="price">
          <text class="money-flag">￥</text>
          <text class="pref">{{order.price_pref}}</text>
          <text class="suff">.{{order.price_suff}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="buying-count">
          x {{inputData.orderNum}}
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class="wrapper display-col" style="position:absolute; bottom:200rpx;">
  <text class="fs-title">友情提醒</text>
  <text class="fs-content">拼团成功后，商品将放入“我的卡包”，可随时享用</text>
</view>
<view class="footer">
  <view class="action">
    <view class="info">
      <view class="buying-price">
        <text class="money-flag">￥</text>
        <text class="pref">{{inputData.orderNum*inputData.price}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <block wx:if="{{!nextBtnDisabled}}">
      <view class="btn" bindtap="gotoNext" data-target="pay" data-price="{{order.price}}">
        <text>选好了</text>
      </view>
    </block>
  </view>
</view>